 Acer’s latest Swift 5 offers superior portability and exceptional performance in an elegant chassis that weighs less than one kilogram. In addition, the device sports a thin-bezeled 14-inch display, which further contributes to the sleekness of this device. Despite its lightweight and portable design, the Acer Swift 5 offers some impressive specifications and can handle professional tasks effortlessly thanks to its Intel 8th-generation processor. Customers also get an impressive 8 hours of battery life, allowing them to do what they need to – whether at home, on the road, or in the office. Thanks to its slim design and impressive features, the Swift 5 is the ideal companion for the travelling professional. The Swift 5’s specifications are detailed in the table below. For more information, visit the Acer website. This article was published in partnership with Acer.